       In the first synopsis form, the getconf utility will write
       to the standard output the value of the variable specified
       by the system_var operand.

       In  the  second  synopsis  form,  the getconf utility will
       write to the standard output the  value  of  the  variable
       specified  by  the path_var operand for the path specified
       by the pathname operand.

